name: Niaz Ahmed
body:
### Hello! I'm Niaz Ahmed

 I am a hardworking and success driven person. Enjoy working in a team and can lead a team to achieve maximum productivity. A quick learner and willing to progress within a company generally driven to success and achievement.

 I come from Rajshahi. Smallest child of Md. Nabirul Alam & Jahanara Meherun Nesa. I have two elder sisters. Completed schools from Rajshahi. Attended engineering College UITS. I love technology and Love to create beautiful design contents. I am an active Rotaractor and love working with a team.
